```

## Basic Usage 基本用法

```php
<?php

use Monolog\Logger;
use Monolog\Handler\StreamHandler;

// create a log channel  创建一个log channel
$log = new Logger('name');
$log->pushHandler(new StreamHandler('path/to/your.log', Logger::WARNING));

// add records to the log 添加records到log
$log->warning('Foo');
$log->error('Bar');
```

